    "title": "Junior SEO Specialist at Shyaway",
    "description": "Shyaway invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of SEO Specialist at our Srinagar location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Shyaway:\nShyaway is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Shyaway!",
